{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:14:15.372Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing Part 5: JSX**\n\nI've made good progress! I've decided to start working on Part 5. Currently, I plan to insert the JSX return block, including the header, banner notice and metrics grid, at line 546 of the file. I am keeping it under 6,000 characters. I've begun designing the header, banner notice and the metrics section.\n\n\n**Drafting Part 5: Structure**\n\nI've moved on from the initial JSX skeleton to structuring the tile grid (the four cards) and filter controls block. I'm focusing on ensuring it stays within the character limit, and I've now drafted a section which includes the narrative header and compliance stitch, all now residing within a parent `div`. I am now focusing on the components of the tile grid.\n\n\n**Analyzing Telemetry Data**\n\nI'm now diving into the specifics, dissecting the provided telemetry data display. I'm focusing on the component structure: I see a global administrative terminal description, a telemetry state indicator with a sync status and epoch reference, and a compliance notice banner. I am interpreting how these are laid out, as well as the styles applied to them. I have now begun to analyze the data's overall visual layout and the role of each element.\n\n\n**Interpreting Visual Structure**\n\nI'm now focusing on the health KPI cards grid and its visual structure. I see a parent `div` with a `grid` class, influencing its layout. I am noting the grid's responsiveness: it changes from one column on smaller screens to four columns on larger screens. I'm focusing on the `gap-4` class to understand the spacing between the cards and the overall arrangement. I am trying to understand the overall architecture so that I can insert the telemetry data.\n\n\n**Examining Metric Components**\n\nI'm now honing in on the Health Index and its related components, focusing on the individual elements and their relationships to one another within the tile. I see a `flex` container with two `div` elements, one displaying the Global Health Index value, and another with a checkmark icon. I'm noting the use of specific classes for styling, such as `text-[9.5px]` and `font-mono`. I am examining the overall visual impact of this section. I am now looking at the core status pulse.\n\n\n**Implementing Status Pulse**\n\nI'm now implementing the status pulse, focusing on integrating the dynamic background colors. I've noted the conditions applied to determine background color assignment based on the index and am evaluating the opacity and hover effect. The objective is to ensure the pulse integrates visually with the telemetry display. I am now evaluating the workspace card for placement.\n\n\n**Integrating Workspace Card**\n\nI'm now integrating the workspace card into the display. I am focusing on the card's composition, observing the arrangement of its elements. I have noted the use of classes for the visual layout, paying close attention to the responsiveness and interactions, especially the hover state and transparency. I am now evaluating the best approach to integrate the card seamlessly within the existing design, maintaining the aesthetic coherence.\n\n\n**Refining Telemetry Display**\n\nI am now focusing on refining the telemetry display components. I am evaluating the use of `WorkspaceCard` and the arrangement of text elements within it. I am also assessing how to integrate new details like latency data and uptime statistics seamlessly into the design. I am giving special attention to visual hierarchy and aesthetics.\n\n\n**Integrating Alert Display**\n\nI'm now integrating the alert display components within the workspace card. I've focused on the styling, observing the use of `className` attributes for visual formatting, typography and colors. I've noted the components for unresolved governance incidents and their alert count display, with its specific use of red color accents. I am also now evaluating the audit escalation details.\n\n\n**Implementing Filter Control**\n\nI'm now implementing the interactive filter control bar. I am working on integrating the filter reset functionality, focusing on handling filter state and managing display conditions. I've designed the visual styling for both the filter bar and the reset button. I'm now evaluating the interaction logic for each filter option, ensuring the display updates are correct.\n\n\n**Integrating Search Field**\n\nI'm now integrating the search field into the filter control bar, focusing on adding the search input and search icon. I've successfully added the input field and its placeholder text. I am now working on the search icon, ensuring it visually aligns correctly within the input field. I'm also now implementing the search query functionality.\n\n\n\n**Adding Client Filter**\n\nI'm now integrating the client filter component into the control bar, focusing on crafting the select element and its associated label. I'm leveraging Tailwind classes to style the text and background, along with the borders and hover effects. I am also implementing the logic for client selection and the display of unique options.\n\n\n\n**Developing Agent Filter**\n\nI'm now focusing on the agent type filter, crafting its select element and label within the control bar. I'm using Tailwind classes for styling, including background, border, hover effects, text, and font. I am working to implement the dynamic population of agent options and link to the filter state.\n\n\n\n**Implementing Status Filter**\n\nI'm now implementing the telemetry status filter within the control bar, building the select element and its associated label. I am using Tailwind classes for styling, including background, border, hover effects, text, and font. I am now focused on dynamically populating the filter with relevant options and linking it to the filter state.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:14:15.389Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"2mktetyc","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/ai-operations/page.tsx","new_text":"\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto pb-12\">\n      {/* --- SECTION 1: NARRATIVE HEADER & COMPLIANCE STITCH --- */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-5\">\n        <div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n            <div className=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] relative flex shrink-0\">\n              <span className={`animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] opacity-75 ${simulationPulse ? \"scale-150\" : \"scale-100\"}`}></span>\n            </div>\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">SOVEREIGN CORE TELEMETRY</span>\n          </div>\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono uppercase mt-1\">AI Operations Command Center</h2>\n          <p className=\"text-xs text-white/55 mt-1 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">\n            Global administrative terminal. Audit multi-agent runtimes, monitor context frame load indices, and coordinate incident ownership across verified hardware enclaves.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 self-start md:self-auto font-mono text-[11px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/35 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-white/60\">\n          <Activity className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2] shrink-0 ${simulationPulse ? \"opacity-100\" : \"opacity-40\"}`} />\n          <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">Telemetry state:</span>\n          <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\">SYNCED</span>\n          <span className=\"text-white/20\">•</span>\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">EPOCH SEC_2026_A</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* --- COMPLIANCE NOTICE BANNER (DO NOT CLAIM LIVE TELEMETRY) --- */}\n      <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/5 to-emerald-500/5 p-4 flex items-start gap-3.5\">\n        <Shield className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n        <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n          <div className=\"text-[11px] font-mono uppercase font-bold text-[#009DFF] tracking-wider\">SIMULATION TELEMETRY STREAM ONLY — Standard sandbox compliance auditing mode active.</div>\n          <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/45 font-mono leading-relaxed max-w-5xl\">\n            This administrative control console operates inside isolated volatile memory spaces. Telemetric streams, CPU partitions (Intel SGX / AMD SEV-SNP), and hardware logs represent verified GFF AI preview models. Actions taken (e.g., owner assignment, diagnostic checks) are modeled locally inside the browser context to demonstrate governance alignment.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* --- SECTION 2: HEALTH KPI CARDS GRID --- */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Global Health Index</span>\n                <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.healthIndex}%</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400\">\n                <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div className=\"space-y-1.5 mt-2\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">\n                <span>Core Status Pulse</span>\n                <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">{overallStats.healthIndex === 100 ? \"OPTIMAL\" : \"STABLE BOUNDS\"}</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-[2.5px] h-2.5 w-full\">\n                {Array.from({ length: 24 }).map((_, idx) => {\n                  let bg = \"bg-[#00FFC2]\";\n                  if (idx === 15) bg = \"bg-amber-400\";\n                  if (idx === 21) bg = \"bg-white/10\";\n                  return (\n                    <div \n                      key={idx} \n                      className={`h-full flex-1 rounded-[1.5px] ${bg} opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity`} \n                      title=\"Micro-Node Telemetry Integrity Check\"\n                    />\n                  );\n                })}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Compute Core Allocation</span>\n                <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.totalThreads} Threads</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF]\">\n                <Cpu className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-1 mt-2\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n                <span>SANDBOX CLUSTERS</span>\n                <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-semibold\">{agents.length} Active Runtimes</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 flex items-center gap-1.5 leading-none\">\n                <TrendingUp className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">+12 Cores</span>\n                <span>since last epoch rotation</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Mean Heartbeat Latency</span>\n                <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.meanLatency} ms</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-[#00FFC2]/20 bg-[#00FFC2]/10 text-[#00FFC2]\">\n                <Clock className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-1 mt-2\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n                <span>ZERO-TRUST TLS WIRE</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white/60 font-medium\">99.998% Uptime</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 leading-none\">\n                Isolated HSM key signatures delay &lt; 2ms\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"relative overflow-hidden group\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between gap-3\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Unresolved Governance Incidents</span>\n                <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#E4000F] tracking-tight font-mono mt-1 block\">{overallStats.activeAlertsCount} Alerts</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-red-500/20 bg-red-500/10 text-red-400\">\n                <AlertTriangle className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-1 mt-2\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n                <span>AUDIT ESCALATIONS</span>\n                <span className=\"text-red-400 font-bold\">1 HIGH PRIORITY</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 leading-none\">\n                Awaiting administrative owner sign-off\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* --- SECTION 3: MASTER INTERACTIVE FILTER CONTROL BAR --- */}\n      <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-2xl bg-[#050505]/20 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 space-y-4\">\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-3 pb-3 border-b border-white/5\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <SlidersHorizontal className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/45\" />\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white/70 tracking-wider\">Telemetry Routing Filters</h3>\n          </div>\n          {(searchQuery || clientFilter !== \"All\" || projectFilter !== \"All\" || agentTypeFilter !== \"All\" || statusFilter !== \"All\" || severityFilter !== \"All\" || ownerFilter !== \"All\") && (\n            <button\n              onClick={handleResetFilters}\n              className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] hover:text-white flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors uppercase font-bold cursor-pointer\"\n            >\n              <X className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n              <span>Reset Filters</span>\n            </button>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-3\">\n          <div className=\"col-span-2 md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Search Node Parameters</label>\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <Search className=\"absolute left-2.5 top-2.5 h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white/35 pointer-events-none\" />\n              <input\n                type=\"text\"\n                placeholder=\"Search agent name, ID, logs...\"\n                value={searchQuery}\n                onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)}\n                className=\"w-full bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] focus:bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/5 focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 rounded-lg pl-8 pr-3 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white outline-none placeholder:text-white/25 transition-all\"\n              />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Client Account</label>\n            <select\n              value={clientFilter}\n              onChange={(e) => setClientFilter(e.target.value)}\n              className=\"w-full bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer appearance-none bg-[#050505]\"\n            >\n              <option value=\"All\">ALL CLIENTS</option>\n              {UNIQUE_CLIENTS.map(c => (\n                <option key={c} value={c}>\n                  {c.replace(\" [Preview Client]\", \"\")}\n                </option>\n              ))}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Project Layer</label>\n            <select\n              value={projectFilter}\n              onChange={(e) => setProjectFilter(e.target.value)}\n              className=\"w-full bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer appearance-none bg-[#050505]\"\n            >\n              <option value=\"All\">ALL PROJECTS</option>\n              {UNIQUE_PROJECTS.map(p => (\n                <option key={p} value={p}>\n                  {p}\n                </option>\n              ))}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Classification</label>\n            <select\n              value={agentTypeFilter}\n              onChange={(e) => setAgentTypeFilter(e.target.value)}\n              className=\"w-full bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer appearance-none bg-[#050505]\"\n            >\n              <option value=\"All\">ALL CLASSIFICATIONS</option>\n              {UNIQUE_TYPES.map(t => (\n                <option key={t} value={t}>\n                  {t}\n                </option>\n              ))}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Telemetry Pulse</label>\n            <select\n              value={statusFilter}\n              onChange={(e) => setStatusFilter(e.target.value)}\n              className=\"w-full bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer appearance-none bg-[#050505]\"\n            >\n              <option value=\"All\">ALL PULSES</option>\n              {UNIQUE_STATUSES.map(s => (\n                <option key={s} value={s} className=\"uppercase font-mono\">\n                  {s.toUpperCase()}\n                </option>\n              ))}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider font-semibold\">Assigned Operator</label>\n            <select\n              value={ownerFilter}\n              onChange={(e) => setOwnerFilter(e.target.value)}\n              className=\"w-full bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 rounded-lg px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all outline-none cursor-pointer appearance-none bg-[#050505]\"\n            >\n              <option value=\"All\">ALL OPERATORS</option>\n              {OWNERS.map(o => (\n                <option key={o} value={o}>\n                  {o}\n                </option>\n              ))}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n","insert_line":546}}}
